5681d","tid":1468330,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:44.000Z","msg":"推上熱門 道歉太難睇"},{"pid":"f139432835a7806af95c42d6eec775c7543e1bb9","tid":1468330,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:18:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"154a3c26c4208bb961dd3a897a25f7ef9a98693d","tid":1468330,"uid":296055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:20:30.000Z","msg":"各位請幫忙分享出去！！！如果你們願意，請幫忙分享以下道歉文章到自己的Facebook,ig,爭取在林鄭講廢話指責我地之前，為811及812中在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉而道歉。並請繼續分享出去！！！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n鑒於這兩天於機場舉行的和平理性機場集會，為各位旅客帶不便，在此，我們真心誠意向各位致歉。<br />\n<br />\nWe would like to sincerely apologize for all the inconvenience caused by the peaceful demonstration at the HK International Airport over the last two days.<br />\n<br />\n我們重申，今次的機場集會，目的為和平理性地引起政府回應及國際關注，希望各位能夠體諒，香港人爭取五大訴求嘅初衷。<br />\n<br />\nOur demonstration aims to peacefully raise the awareness of the global community, as well as response from the HK government on the five demands from the public of Hong Kong. We thank you for your tolerance and understanding.<br />\n<br />\n我們再次向在場記者，救護人員，機場職員及旅客等受影響人士致歉，感謝各位的諒解。<br />\n<br />\nTo all the reporters, ambulance staff, airport staff and affected passengers, we again would like to express oir deepest apology to all the inconvenience and disruptions<br />\n<br />\n感謝所有仍堅持初心嘅香港人<br />\n<br />\n一群等待政府回應訴求的香港人"},{"pid":"6a155d9bf10f27354b454e349731b383f53e159f","tid":1468330,"uid":65213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea80fa98dd96817c8a77cb5f03fe0a1b1fbe110d","tid":1468330,"uid":260180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:22:57.000Z","msg":"試下講 : 謹代表香港政府 向各國旅客致歉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468526</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb047a3db1ecd0c952c5d6a4ff3c18a935f02a92","tid":1468330,"uid":12039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:11.000Z","msg":"其實真係好基本嘅pr手段黎<br />\n香港人要識玩啊<br />\n同無賴鬥只講手段不講道理（當然係暗啞底嘅做法）<br />\nWe apologise for government&rsquo;s poor arrangement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40753c48aeb7d9c0192209fcfbbcef6c244732a5","tid":1468330,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:41.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"4cc8d44e33f988e7429cf9ac7ca7d5b1eab4b37e","tid":1468330,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:24:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1da5fdf614b9442d2e76c5c825c515bd5e04eca","tid":1468330,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f496652234ebe4e11505c37f657b071cbbdc9575","tid":1468330,"uid":53321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:15.000Z","msg":"加油 大家加油"},{"pid":"d8a3774d604a5d8d2b05b3c2ed5203457400847a","tid":1468330,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:19.000Z","msg":"我哋需要一份聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc22cc947e93c1e34a3271cc71d230972be715e9","tid":1468330,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:37.000Z","msg":"記住所有手足共識：<br />\n1. 不傷害記者，不阻礙記者工作<br />\n2. 不傷害急救人員，不阻礙急救人員工作<br />\n3. 不任意攻擊一般平民及其財產<br />\n4. 不使用酷刑<br />\n<br />\n如果有人太激動破壞共識，拉開佢一邊先<br />\n死都唔聽，有機會係狗扮示威者帶風向<br />\n獨立思考，唔好中伏<br />\n<br />\n入嚟睇打狗GIF開心返啦大家<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468590\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468590</a><br />\n<br />\nFACT CHECKED 機場係春袋，要大大力錫落去<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468243</a>"},{"pid":"b021f6a1b2cc8ec2980b637f2659bd470dc55df7","tid":1468330,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:25:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d376c9ea8b0f2a858f01e72532f5bc92b056a470","tid":1468330,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:12.000Z","msg":"聽日要派糖 但絕對唔可以道歉!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDHvAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDHvAS</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英文:<br />\nWe, Hong Kong protesters, on behalf of the Hong Kong Government and the PRC, apologize to...... <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住記住 派野食野飲!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"1de7af82997286bfdc29aef73c90f0ad7154b6f2","tid":1468330,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:26:15.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太有見地<br />\n<br />\n#我係禮貌撚<br />\n#我係道歉撚 #代香港政府道歉 #要抗爭 撳錢就得<br />\n<br />\n[幫推]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468330/page/1</a><br />\n&quot;對唔住呀，我地個政府好撚衰，我代佢道歉&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467893/page/1</a><br />\n對政府不合作 唔係對市民不合作<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球道歉運動! <br />\n推到去&quot;民間記者會&quot;.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1467782/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nSay 句 Sorry, 好易啫 ~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma